Package org.javamoney.cdi.api

Contains the annotations to refine the javamoney artifacts that can be injected.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AmountSpec
    Annotation that allows to optionally refine a MonetaryAmountFactory, MonetaryAmount or MonetaryAmountFactoryQuery to be injected.
    ConversionSpec
    Annotation that allows to optionally refine a CurrencyConversion, ExchangeRateProvider or ConversionQuery to be injected.
    CurrencySpec
    Annotation that allows to define a CurrencyQuery or an CurrencyUnit to be injected.
    FormatSpec
    Annotation that allows to define a MonetaryAmountFormat or AmountFormatQuery to be injected.

Package org.javamoney.cdi.api Description

Contains the annotations to refine the javamoney artifacts that can be injected.
